These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, go
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person playing go is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Game   | go    | monopoly |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
2 different games are played: whist, bridge
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the canadian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian  |
| Game     | bridge   | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | collecting   | writing  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | iced-tea  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, baking
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Hobby   | baking   | video-games   |
| Transport     | train       | ship      |

